            </div>
    
            <div class="boximage" style="overflow: auto; background-color: lavenderblush;">
                <img src="/images/inspiredimage.jpg">
                <h3>Inspired Designs</h3>
                <p>Our inspiration for creating this website came from our own experiences as both tourists and locals. We've always been drawn to the unique and one-of-a-kind products that can only be found in local shops and markets, and we wanted to create a platform that would make it easier for others to discover these hidden gems.
                </p>
            </div>
            
